diagrams.description: IBM Cloud Pak System Software for Power is an IBM Cloud Pak System solution that provides hybrid cloud capabilities. It is an integrated, highly-scalable private cloud appliance that helps you to build, deploy, and manage workloads that are based on IBM Cloud Power VS.
